ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#49: FILE: drivers/scsi/osst.c:1407:
+	if ((buffer = vmalloc((nframes + 1) * OS_DATA_SIZE)) == NULL)

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

